t.heres the lineup; Frankensteins monster,his mate(voiced by Phyllis diller)Dracula,the werewolf,the mummy,the creature,the hunchback,Dr Jekyll and Mr Hyde,invisible man,and it (a king Kong lookalike)its a wild monster party with a singing group of skeletons modeled after the Beatles,well remember this is 1968.its a marvel of animation done way before any computer graphics were even thought of.this has always been an ageless personal favorite.even Tim Burton was inspired by mad monster party when he did nightmare before Christmas.10 out of 10 check it out,its a good Halloween party movie.\r\n","name":"Mad Monster Party?","name_cn":"怪兽大聚会","tags":[{"name":"无","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1969","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画电影","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"空","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"怪兽大聚会"},{"key":"上映年度","value":"1969-03-08"},{"key":"片长","value":"94 分钟"},{"key":"话数","value":"1"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":3,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":0,"6":0,"7":2,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":1,"dropped":3,"wish":1,"collect":7,"doing":2},"id":113093,"eps":1,"meta_tags":["剧场版"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2}]